high_descs: Take a step to the right to face the sink.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Turn around and walk to the right to face the potato on the counter.
Cut the potato on the counter into slices.
Step to the right and face the counter by the coffee maker.
Place the knife on the counter.
Step to the left to face the potato on the counter.
Pick up a slice of potato on the counter.
Step to the right and look up to face the microwave.
Heat the potato slice in the microwave and remove it.
Turn around and walk to the left to face the trash can.
Place the potato slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To heat a potato slice and place it in the trash can.

high_descs: Walk to the sink in front of you.
Take the knife with the yellow handle out of the sink.
Turn around and walk towards the white table then turn right and walk to the counter with the plate on it.
Cut the potato on the counter.
Turn around then turn left and walk towards the counter in front of you, turn left to the counter with the coffee maker on it.
Put the knife on the counter.
Turn right and walk past the stove then turn right and face the counter with the potato on it.
Pick up a slice of potato from the counter.
Go to the stove on your right.
Cook the potato in the microwave above the stove then take the potato out.
Turn around and walk towards the white door then turn left to the trash can next to the fridge.
Put the potato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw the cooked potato into the trash.

high_descs: Take a step forward to the sink.
Pick the knife up from inside the sink.
Go to the cutting board on the left side of the stove.
Cut the potato to the right of the cutting board.
Go to the counter on the right side of the stove.
Put the knife down in front of the coffee machine.
Go back over to the cutting board where the potato was.
Pick up a slice of the potato.
Go to the front of the stove with the potato slice.
Cook the potato slice in the microwave over the stove, then take it out again.
Go to the trash can that's on the floor on the right of the sink.
Put the potato slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a piece of cooked potato.
